{"tid":839490,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"意甲榜首大戰77台免費播","createTime":"2018-09-28T03:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T12:56:10.000Z","uid":53484,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3a0fe9e646cff748de84ee53fcb34294ec51937e","tid":839490,"uid":53484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T03:45:31.000Z","msg":"【意甲榜首大戰77台免費播】<br />\n<br />\n星期六晚12點，意甲將會上演祖雲達斯對拿玻里嘅榜首大戰。榜首嘅祖雲達斯喺C朗帶領下暫時6戰全勝，而拿玻里亦拎住5勝1負緊隨其後。呢場榜首大戰份量十足，奇妙電視77台亦會免費直播，意甲球迷留意了。"},{"pid":"cf810a8a6a2e2c1c7e20ba67d7cf675b62ebc263","tid":839490,"uid":161311,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T03:47:27.000Z","msg":"意假嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e642153d2c672a6217be5de51d99495eba8cd0","tid":839490,"uid":4525,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T03:49:27.000Z","msg":"王騎ready"},{"pid":"bf5236413a6177cf38bcb92f2c3ba1d68f0de57b","tid":839490,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:01:43.000Z","msg":"官網播唔播？追唔撚到佢個閪台"},{"pid":"d813ea1c9c107bfb14d2980c8ddb3cde8c04fe50","tid":839490,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf5236413a6177cf38bcb92f2c3ba1d68f0de57b","tid":839490,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:01:43.000Z","msg":"官網播唔播？追唔撚到佢個閪台"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:03:43.000Z","msg":"官網播<br />\ndelay慢過電視喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3cc14bf5d2285edd1fd82c5ee61e11698eeea6","tid":839490,"uid":154385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:00:18.000Z","msg":"祖雲達斯喺C朗帶領下暫時6戰全勝?<br />\n<br />\n有場食牌落場坐"},{"pid":"5afd0a0f0da2c5e2c3846ff97ac66c1b3c0ed3a1","tid":839490,"uid":10975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d3cc14bf5d2285edd1fd82c5ee61e11698eeea6","tid":839490,"uid":154385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score